source: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_SEQ_00<tab>Just because 789th Order Craftsman Bo Gu can't be bothered to mine a vein does not mean someone else can, no, no!
target: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_SEQ_00<tab>Im Abbaugebiet des 789. Ordens ersinnt der gewiefte Bo Gu ein Attentat.

source: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_SEQ_01<tab>There is a pickman of rare talent in the 59th Order Dig, and 789th Order Craftsman Bo Gu would like him dead for the sin of success─his own as well as that of his associate, 13th Order Fugleman Zo Ga. Oblige him by completing the FATE “The Miner in the Mirror” and presenting the resulting proof of your deed to Bo Gu.
target: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_SEQ_01<tab>Ein berühmter Bergmann des 59. Ordens, Hauer Be Ze, arbeitet für den Despoten Zo Ga und füllt rasant dessen Kriegskasse mit seltenem Golderz. Treib ihm in dem FATE „Riecher für Erz“ am Eisensee vor dem Eingang zu den U'Ghamaro-Minen sein unglaubliches Gespür für seltene Metalle aus! Dabei wirst du <var 32 ((Item)) 02F21E75020502 /var> erbeuten, die du Bo Gu als Beweis deines Erfolgs vorlegen kannst.

source: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_SEQ_02<tab>You deliver the Titan mythrilshield to Bo Gu, though in truth, the craftsman need not have suspected you of reticence. The now-dead pickman was hardly the maestro of the mines that Bo Gu made him out to be, and was a nasty piece of work you were happy to put six fulms under.
target: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_SEQ_02<tab><var 2B ((<var 32 ((Item)) 03F21E75020202 /var>)) /var> ist ein untrügliches Zeichen deines Triumphes über <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F205F4020502 /var>. Der erfahrene Bergmann wird so schnell kein Golderz mehr für Zo Ga sammeln, was einen erheblichen Rückschlag für den ehrgeizigen Kobold-Anführer bedeutet. Bo Gu ist erleichtert und dankbar für deine Hilfe.

source: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_TODO_00<tab>Deliver the Titan mythrilshield obtained in the FATE “The Miner in the Mirror” to Bo Gu.
target: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_TODO_00<tab>Bei dem FATE „Riecher für Erz“ <var 32 ((Item)) 02F21E75020502 /var> erobern und Bo Gu zeigen

source: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_000<tab>Zo Ga do I hate, yes, yes, that Zo Ga is truly worthy of my loathing. It is unfair─inequitable, deranged, unfair─that he should have so much gil for all that work he does. Ugh!
target: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_000<tab>Grrr ... grrrmpf ... <knirsch> Zo Ga ich hasse! Mieser Unterdrücker! Einen berühmten Kobold-Bergmann er in seine Dienste gestellt hat.

source: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_001<tab>Now I hear he has recruited a pickman of note─renown, respect, note! This Be Ze is not like miners of our dear 789th, no. This one has struck vein after vein of soft and shiny gold! Gold is his gift, yes, yes.
target: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_001<tab><var 2B ((<var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F205F4020202 /var>)) /var>! Guten Riecher für Golderz er hat! Unauffindbare Goldadern er findet!

source: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_002<tab>They say he'll not work for just any fugleman. They say he serves only kobolds of great acumen. Well, <var 1A 02 /var>they<var 1A 01 /var> can go sup on hot candle wax and die in the privy! With this master pickman serving him, Zo Ga will prosper─flourish, thrive, prosper!
target: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_002<tab>Schnell, schnell, sein Gespür für edle Metalle du ihm austreibst! Sonst er lässt Zo Gas Kriegskasse wachsen und wachsen! Dann er uns noch stärker unterdrückt!

source: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_003<tab>We cannot allow this, no, no. But lucky for us, a dead master has no gifts! No difference between clever dead and dafty dead, except it vexes more to lose a good thing. Yes, Zo Ga will be vexed─chagrined, annoyed, vexed!
target: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_003<tab><var 2B ((<var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F205F4020502 /var>)) /var> du besiegst, ja? Schnell, schnell! Kein Gold für Zo Ga er soll finden.

source: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_004<tab>The adventurer is not convinced, <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> is not persuaded to this cause. Will the adventurer take the gil but not do the deed? A proof, yes, yes, a proof you shall bring!
target: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_004<tab>Als Belohnung für seine Dienste <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F205F4020502 /var> hat bekommen <var 32 ((Item)) 02F21E75020502 /var>. Große Auszeichnung unter Kobolden!

source: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_005<tab>Loathsome Zo Ga paid Be Ze a healthy sum─yes, yes, one Titan mythrilshield─when the pesky pickman joined his dig, a gift he gave him for the seams he would find. The adventurer will bring this coin─perhaps covered in innocent ichor?
target: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_005<tab>Die du eroberst und mir zeigst, ja? Sonst ich dir nicht glauben kann, dass du großen <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F205F4020502 /var> besiegt hast, nein, nein.

source: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_010<tab>The adventurer returns from the slaughter, from the killing <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> is coming! Does <var 08 E905 ((she)) ((he)) /var> bring a token─sign, proof, token?
target: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_010<tab><var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F205F4020502 /var> du hast besiegt, ja? Dann <var 32 ((Item)) 03F21E75020502 /var> du mir zeigst, ja?

source: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_011<tab>The proof, yes, yes! As good as your word you have been, yes, you are to be trusted with murders most foul! Perhaps even Zo Ga himself someday...
target: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_011<tab>Oh ja, ja! Hübsch, hübsch! Kein Zweifel! Siegreich du warst.

source: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_012<tab>Horrible, he is, that Zo Ga! Burrows in the richest seams like a tick at a teat, and won't share with us who come late and do no work!
target: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_012<tab>Kein Golderz nie mehr nicht <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F205F4020202 /var> für Zo Ga wird finden. Toll, toll!

source: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_013<tab>But the adventurer has given me some food for thought...food, yummy food. Everything Zo Ga has can go splat or boom, smooth or chunky. There is much hope, yes, yes, Zo Ga has much cause for concern!
target: TEXT_BANKOB202_01336_BOGU_000_013<tab>Ganz erleichtert ich bin! Zo Ga eine Spitzhacke zwischen die Füße du geworfen hast. Danke, danke!
